      "id": "PopularPost33579",
      "post_content": "A red [Fog](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Fog) / [Holy Day](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Holy Day) / [Darkness](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Darkness) effect, cute!\n  \nLet's add a red one to that bunch called Smoke or something and a blue version as well, then we've got a complete cycle of a timeshifted version for an effect in each color :D",
